defs.name: settle_access_control
defs.docs: Settlement access control. Ensures RFQ is:

attributes.value: / Settlement access control. Ensures RFQ is:
/ 1. RFQ has not yet been settled if taker
/ 2. Order has not yet been settled if maker
/ 3. If last look is required then RFQ is approved

defs.name: last_look_access_control
defs.docs: Last look access control. Ensures last look:

attributes.value: / Last look access control. Ensures last look:
/ 1. Last looks is configured for RFQ
/ 2. Order belongs to authority approving via last look

defs.docs: Response access control. Ensures response satisfies the following conditions:

attributes.value: / Response access control. Ensures response satisfies the following conditions:
/ 1. RFQ authority is not the same as maker authority
/ 3. Response bid/ask match request order side
/ 4. Response bid/ask amount is greater than 0

defs.name: return_collateral_access_control
defs.docs: Return collateral access control. Ensures returning collateral for RFQ that is:

attributes.value: / Return collateral access control. Ensures returning collateral for RFQ that is:
/ 1. Collateral has not already by returned
/ 3. If RFQ is not confirmed either expired or order has been confirmed
